Russia is not actually a very nice place to liveIt may have impressed Tucker Carlson, but it's still a dysfunctional middle-income country. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/ Russia-is-not-actually-a-very-nice https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/ Russia-is-not-actually-a-very-niceNoah Smith Wed, 14 Feb 2024 23:29:26 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg" width="718" height="479.8173076923077" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:973,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:718,&quot;bytes&quot;:156971,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33aff4df-9829-4a9c-95be-cfef192e8537_1500x1002.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=51584358">摄影</a>： <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Mstyslav_Chernov">Mstyslav Chernov</a> ， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/?ref=openverse">CC BY-SA 4.0</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>塔克·卡尔森最近从俄罗斯旅行回来<a href="https://twitter.com/CollinRugg/status/1757093756036354223">，对所见所闻感到惊讶</a>。他将莫斯科与美国城市进行了比较：</p><blockquote><p>对我来说，最激进、非常令人震惊和非常不安的是莫斯科市，我从未去过那里，它是欧洲最大的城市……比我国家的任何城市都好得多。我不知道……例如，如果你不能使用地铁，就像纽约市的许多人因为太危险而害怕的那样，你必须想知道，这不是领导力的最终衡量标准吗？ ......对于一个美国人来说去莫斯科是激进的。我不知道。这周我在新加坡、东京、迪拜和阿布扎比了解到了这一点，因为这些城市，无论我们如何被告知它们的运作方式以及它们的运作原则是什么，都是美好的居住地没有猖獗的通货膨胀。</p></blockquote><p>现在，他对东京和新加坡的看法肯定是正确的（我从未去过迪拜或阿布扎比，所以我无法发表评论）。他对许多其他外国城市的看法也是正确的。与大多数发达国家相比，美国城市破败、肮脏、危险，公共交通系统更差，犯罪率更高。新加坡的谋杀率为每10万人0.1人；纽约市是美国<a href="https://247wallst.com/special-report/2024/02/06/new-york-has-one-of-the-lowest-gun-crime-rates-in-the-us/">最安全的大城市</a>，谋杀率为4.8，是新加坡的50多倍。猖獗的邻避主义和高昂的建筑成本使纽约远比欧洲或亚洲发达地区的城市低俗，而中西部的老工业城市则因投资减少和高犯罪率而被掏空。美国的城市状况不佳，我们的社会应该大力推动改善它们。</p><p>话虽如此，莫斯科并不是进行比较的最佳选择。尽管石油收入在过去二十年里不断涌入，但这座城市仍然有一种严峻的后苏联氛围。航拍镜头显示了一个小型中央商务区，有几座新建的摩天大楼，周围是一望无际的严峻的苏联时代公寓社区，巨大的道路和高速公路纵横交错，到处都是空地，偶尔还有俗气的纪念碑： </p><div id="youtube2-eL3-StQ9ijM" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;eL3-StQ9ijM&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/eL3-StQ9ijM?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>莫斯科唯一真正伟大的事情是它的地铁，它通常被认为是<a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/moscow-metro-russia-versus-nyc-subway-photos-2019-7">世界上最好的地铁之一</a>，并以其美丽的车站而闻名。</p><p>犯罪率怎么样？据官方统计，<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_federal_subjects_of_Russia_by_murder_rate">莫斯科 2017 年的谋杀率</a>（我能找到广泛报道的数据的最后一年）为 2.5，这意味着它的危险程度约为纽约的一半。但有理由怀疑这个数字，因为有证据表明俄罗斯在普京领导下误报了其谋杀率。</p><p>官方统计数据显示，自1999年普京上台以来，<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/1045368/homicide-rate-in-russia/">俄罗斯的谋杀率急剧下降。</a>上世纪90年代，俄罗斯的谋杀率飙升——2001年为每10万人30.7人。这大约是费城谋杀率的 1.5 倍，费城是美国最危险的城市之一。这是<em>整个国家</em>的数字，而不是大城市或暴力特别严重的地区的数字。早在2001年，俄罗斯的谋杀率是美国整体的<em>5倍多</em>。</p><p>在普京的领导下，官方谋杀率大幅下降。截至 2022 年，该数字为 3.7，低于美国。但<a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/276963892_What_is_Russia's_real_homicide_rate_Statistical_reconstruction_and_the_'decivilizing_process'">Lysova 和 Shchitov（2015）</a>认为，这一下降的部分原因仅仅是因为警方报告的谋杀案减少了。他们指出，在 2000 年代谋杀案数量下降的同时，卫生统计数据中记录的“身份不明的尸体”数量却在飙升： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg" width="890" height="525" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:525,&quot;width&quot;:890,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:37497,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d07e7d8-f698-45b3-9e7f-b7c533b5f79b_890x525.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/276963892_What_is_Russia's_real_homicide_rate_Statistical_reconstruction_and_the_'decivilizing_process'">Lysova 和 Shchitov (2015)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>作者列出了俄罗斯警方有动机少报谋杀案的许多原因，但最重要的似乎只是来自弗拉基米尔·普京本人的政治压力。普京将法律和秩序作为他的政府和 2000 年代言论的关键主题；这大概会导致公共安全有所改善，但也可能会激励全国各地的警察部门表现出虚假的进步。</p><p>联合国和世界银行对此表示同意。他们的统计数据显示，俄罗斯的凶杀率大幅下降，但到 2021 年仅降至每 10 万人中 7 人左右： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg" width="916" height="779" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:779,&quot;width&quot;:916,&quot;resizeW