是，一些保守派似乎使无尽的游行变得荒谬。除了洛瑞（Lowry）外，还有候选人尼基·海莉（Nikki Haley），他也不禁嘲笑反鞭打权，并宣布我们需要“<a href="https://twitter.com/NikkiHaley/status/1753230029633286362">使美国再次正常</a>”。</p><p>听到，听到。</p><h4> 2.政治是否被性别战争接管？没那么快……</h4><p>现在是时候播放<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-not-to-be-fooled-by-viral-charts">病毒</a>图表了！出色的约翰·伯恩·穆尔多奇（John Burn-Murdoch）最近分享了一张大型病毒的图表。它显示了发达国家年轻男女的政治倾向最近的巨大差异： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1076748f-1309-4d32-8617-1643fcdb1509_921x805.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1076748f-1309-4d32-8617-1643fcdb1509_921x805.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1076748f-1309-4d32-8617-1643fcdb1509_921x805.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1076748f-1309-4d32-8617-1643fcdb1509_921x805.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1076748f-1309-4d32-8617-1643fcdb1509_921x805.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1076748f-1309-4d32-8617-1643fcdb1509_921x805.jpeg" width="636" height="555.8957654723127" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-me