n></figure></div><p>的确，这是一个令人不安的趋势。但是，它可能不存在。 Burn-Murdoch的数据来自各种可靠的数据源。但是，此问题还有其他数据源，它们似乎并没有显示出相同的差异。<a href="https://www.allendowney.com/blog/2024/01/28/is-the-ideology-gap-growing/">艾伦·唐尼（Allen Downey）着眼</a>于仅美国的数据源，一般社会调查，发现一个非常适中的差异： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg" width="903" height="681" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d78b29fc-558c-40aa-ba06-0eb81f2e527d_903x681.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:nul